{"tid":1553040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2019年香港自殺資料統計 簡要數據","createTime":"2019-09-08T13:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T16:01:27.000Z","uid":4273,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f93f8676e8c7c11dfa1737799b1a271ddb2afe","tid":1553040,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:09:40.000Z","msg":"2019年截至9月8日中午12時，自殺個案共錄得733宗(743人)，當中有504宗(509人)因此而死亡，平均每天發生2.92宗(2.96人)個案。【圖一】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T6a5fvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT6a5fvq.jpg&h=19f55af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男性佔整體個案佔62%(461人)，原因最多是健康問題，其次是財政問題；而女性則佔38%(282人)，原因最多都是健康問題，其次是感情問題。30-34歲年齡組別最為嚴重，其次是50-54歲，綜合個案絕大部份是健康問題，當中包括精神病及情緒病而影響。【圖二】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wSYOdg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwSYOdg9.jpg&h=f0b27b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以區議會分區分佈個案百分佔比最嚴重的是觀塘區佔9.96%，其次是油尖旺區及沙田區均佔8.05%，接著是深水埗區佔7.50%。個案率最嚴重的是油尖旺區佔17.99%，每10萬人中有18人自殺，其次是中西區佔16.56%，每10萬人中有16.6人自殺，接著是深水埗區佔13.98%，每10萬人中有14人自殺。【圖三】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6JOdhb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6JOdhb.jpg&h=2ad0a7a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2019年香港自殺資料統計</ins></strong><br />\n本文件旨在記錄香港每日由新聞報導之自殺數據，以便用作討論。<br />\n本文件並非鼓吹自殺行為，請珍惜生命，關心身邊家人及朋友。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicide&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=0ff86cb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicide</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideHTML&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=acd46ca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideHTML</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.siuyeong.com%2F2019HKsuicideAPI&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=e2c7f6b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.siuyeong.com/2019HKsuicideAPI</a>"},{"pid":"2c4cedc6e936c9ef59ab25f1d36b9b33d9ad42c8","tid":1553040,"uid":154039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e99a94ef827c118fa126d6aa13cecd53aaa4b2fc","tid":1553040,"uid":109538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"其他年分呢？有無2000-2019數據"},{"pid":"3fb9e8fd63b5cc06069cbcf71cbab69d5d9b5fb9","tid":1553040,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e99a94ef827c118fa126d6aa13cecd53aaa4b2fc","tid":1553040,"uid":109538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"其他年分呢？有無2000-2019數據"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:16:35.000Z","msg":"你好 冇的<br />\n<br />\n我係由2019年開始自行記錄～"},{"pid":"b4a39ed662cb20493f731c287a67e3af82e88880","tid":1553040,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"我都想死"},{"pid":"9eaaa2be0fe0d125c4266b123ccfb6c8054b12e8","tid":1553040,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4a39ed662cb20493f731c287a67e3af82e88880","tid":1553040,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"我都想死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>防止自殺求助熱線：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康 網上支援平台「Open噏」： <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=603ecbf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"6b68764b47075ac3cf129d0cb695342bd5aefe84","tid":1553040,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T14:42:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>防止自殺求助熱線：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康 網上支援平台「Open噏」： <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=603ecbf4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a>"},{"pid":"5cbdf027bd2a646ad53f698aedcca71d6cff491e","tid":1553040,"uid":171272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n好多謝您，我嫲嫲今年走左。我本身父母離左婚，我同啊哥住，同嫲嫲感情好好。<br />\n佢走左之後啊爸係一個月後嘅喪禮上淨係肯同我暗示嫲嫲係自殺（因為嫲嫲遺書有講唔想親人知，所以我都追問左好耐先知係自殺，但都係唔知詳細）。<br />\n之後我一直放唔低，有上網搵過兇宅資料，但完全搵唔到（因為我一直都係search住址，而佢根本唔係屋企走）。<br />\n今日咁啱有個老師share左你呢個post, 我終於搵到關於嫲嫲走嘅資料，嫲嫲個姓好特別，年齡、地區、自殺原因都吻合，所以應該無錯。<br />\n<br />\nSor 我有啲語無倫次，但多得巴打你整理左啲資料，我先搵得番篇報導。好多謝您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a06b596e034ee7a86c79274f8a9ac37bf70656c","tid":1553040,"uid":171272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:04:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2995783049b39d1574be0932a57118a2cfc60c06","tid":1553040,"uid":4273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cbdf027bd2a646ad53f698aedcca71d6cff491e","tid":1553040,"uid":171272,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n好多謝您，我嫲嫲今年走左。我本身父母離左婚，我同啊哥住，同嫲嫲感情好好。<br />\n佢走左之後啊爸係一個月後嘅喪禮上淨係肯同我暗示嫲嫲係自殺（因為嫲嫲遺書有講唔想親人知，所以我都追問左好耐先知係自殺，但都係唔知詳細）。<br />\n之後我一直放唔低，有上網搵過兇宅資